{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/investors/layout,_N_T_/investors/page,_N_T_/investors"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/investors/__PAGE__","/investors","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"__variable_188709 __variable_9a8899 h-full antialiased\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/d12b145465f96dee.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-6bbc21fc53639a8a.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-215e5051988c3dde.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/794-2e9f20eba326fbe9.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-a00441ad7ebde43a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/9da6db1e-a9775a91962987a2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/810-3a26241d106256ce.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-680e7607e7921dbe.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/investors/page-47a069167e25da70.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Crowvo | Private Social Communities That Drive Real Events</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Crowvo is a privacy-first social platform where communities chat, grow, and turn online energy into real-world events.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?603d046c9a6fdfbb\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-slate-200/80 bg-white/85 backdrop-blur-xl dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-[#0b0d14]/85\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 sm:px-6\"><a class=\"text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Crowvo</a><nav class=\"hidden gap-6 text-sm text-muted md:flex\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/investors\">Investors</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/admin\">Admin</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><button class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-foreground shadow-sm backdrop-blur hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-white/10 dark:hover:bg-white/20\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\">Light<!-- --> mode</button><a data-analytics-event=\"cta_start_hub_click\" data-analytics-cta=\"navbar_start_hub\" class=\"rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#5865F2] to-[#7c5cff] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white transition hover:scale-105\" href=\"/#waitlist\">Start Your Hub</a></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-8 px-4 py-12 sm:px-6\"><section class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-[#151a2b]/85\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.16em] text-indigo-500 dark:text-indigo-300\">INVESTOR ACCESS</p><h1 class=\"mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl\">Crowvo Investor Brief</h1><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-muted\">Crowvo is building the privacy-first social OS for communities, with event discovery and conversion embedded directly in the social graph.</p></section><section class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\"><article class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-[#151a2b]/70\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Problem</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted\">Communities spend daily attention in chat tools that are not designed to convert social energy into coordinated action. Discovery, planning, and attendance remain fragmented.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-[#151a2b]/70\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Solution</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted\">Crowvo replaces Discord for action-oriented communities by combining private hubs, social feed, live chat, and event conversion flows in one product.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-[#151a2b]/70\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Market Opportunity</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted\">We sit at the intersection of live events, creator communities, and social media, targeting a large and growing engagement + transaction market with stronger retention from community-driven loops.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-[#151a2b]/70\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Vision</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted\">Become the default private social layer where communities build daily habit and turn momentum into real-world outcomes.</p></article></section><section class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-[#151a2b]/70\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Request deck access</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted\">Submit interest to receive the deck, traction updates, and early diligence materials.</p></div><form class=\"space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-white/5\"><input required=\"\" placeholder=\"Full name\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-black/30 dark:text-white\" name=\"name\"/><input required=\"\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-black/30 dark:text-white\" name=\"email\"/><input required=\"\" placeholder=\"Fund / Angel group\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-black/30 dark:text-white\" name=\"company\"/><input placeholder=\"Typical check size (optional)\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-black/30 dark:text-white\" name=\"checkSize\"/><textarea name=\"message\" required=\"\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Tell us what you&#x27;d like to learn.\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-black/30 dark:text-white\"></textarea><button type=\"submit\" data-analytics-event=\"cta_request_deck_click\" data-analytics-cta=\"investor_form_submit\" class=\"h-11 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-500 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Request Investor Brief</button></form></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-slate-200/80 bg-white/80 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-[#0b0d14]/60\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-2 px-4 py-8 text-sm text-muted sm:px-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Crowvo. Social communities first, events built in.</p><p>Built for founders, creators, and city explorers.</p></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-6bbc21fc53639a8a.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[9283,[\\\"229\\\",\\\"static/chunks/9da6db1e-a9775a91962987a2.js\\\",\\\"810\\\",\\\"static/chunks/810-3a26241d106256ce.js\\\",\\\"558\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/lay